{"id":["110744751894024014"],"username":["nixkelley"],"acct":["nixkelley@firefish.lgbt"],"display_name":["Nix Kelley"],"locked":[false],"bot":[false],"discoverable":[true],"group":[false],"created_at":["2023-07-20"],"note":["<p><span>Thinker of profound thoughts &amp; also shitposts.<br><br><\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Trans\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Trans<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Non-Binary\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Non-Binary<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/GenderQueer\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#GenderQueer<\/a><span>. <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Neurodivergent\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Neurodivergent<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Writer\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Writer<\/a><span>. <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Disabled\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Disabled<\/a><span> with <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/ChronicIllness\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#ChronicIllness<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/MCAS\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#MCAS<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/EDS\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#EDS<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/POTS\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#POTS<\/a><span>. <br><br>I write about <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/QueerIdentity\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#QueerIdentity<\/a><span>, <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Death\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Death<\/a><span>, <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Hope\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Hope<\/a><span>, <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Praxis\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Praxis<\/a><span>, &amp; <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/SongLyrics\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#SongLyrics<\/a><span> at <\/span><b><span>the Infinite<\/span><\/b><span> at <\/span><a href=\"https://nixkelley.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://nixkelley.com<\/a><span>. My inspiration to write usually comes when songs and poetry remind me what is true. <br><br>I currently live on Anishinaabeg land in what is called Michigan, in the lower half of the mitten, between the Great Lakes.<br><br>I am a trained <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/DeathDoula\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#DeathDoula<\/a><span>. I engage in <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/DeathWork\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#DeathWork<\/a><span> and <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/GriefWork\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#GriefWork<\/a><span> for my community, using a reciprocity model rather than a capitalist structure. I write <\/span><b><span>Paths That Lead Home<\/span><\/b><span>, essays for the dying and their loved ones, which you can sign up for at <\/span><a href=\"https://pathsthatleadhome.com/subscribe/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://pathsthatleadhome.com/subscribe/<\/a><span><br><br>I'm currently training in a pre-Gardnerian Celtic oathbound lineaged oral mystery tradition of <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/BritishTraditionalWitchcraft\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#BritishTraditionalWitchcraft<\/a><span>. I serve the community wherever I live (and wherever I can travel digitally), as a layperson for now and as clergy once I reach an appropriate level of training. <br><br>I am a <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/pagan\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#pagan<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/polytheist\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#polytheist<\/a><span> and <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/animist\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#animist<\/a><span>. I live in an intentional community with my <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/ChosenFamily\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#ChosenFamily<\/a><span>, and we are learning how to do this as we go, taking inspiration from ancient Celtic ideas of communal living.<br><br>I'm a <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/gamer\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#gamer<\/a><span>. My current rotation of PC games is <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/IXION\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#IXION<\/a><span>, <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/MaskOfTheRose\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#MaskOfTheRose<\/a><span>, <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/OxygenNotIncluded\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#OxygenNotIncluded<\/a><span>, &amp; <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/LOTRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#LOTRO<\/a><span>. I have a deep love for <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/DeathStranding\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#DeathStranding<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Fallout4\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Fallout4<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/ESO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#ESO<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Skyrim\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Skyrim<\/a><span> &amp; <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/Frostpunk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Frostpunk<\/a><span>. On the Switch, I'm playing <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/CozyGrove\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#CozyGrove<\/a><span> <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/OregonTrail\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#OregonTrail<\/a><span> &amp; <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/NotTonight\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#NotTonight<\/a><span>.<br><br>I'm a <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/knitter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#knitter<\/a><span> &amp; my Ravelry profile is <\/span><a href=\"https://ravelry.com/people/nixkelley\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://ravelry.com/people/nixkelley<\/a><span><br><br>I am a <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/polyam\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#polyam<\/a><span> person and I currently have two partners. I watch queer media whenever possible. I love ridiculous <\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/paranormal\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#paranormal<\/a><span> media. My favorite kind of humor is dark.<br><br><\/span><a href=\"https://firefish.lgbt/tags/AltText\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#AltText<\/a><span> is the rule: <br>Avatar is a selfie I took, framing my face and one of my tattooed arms. I have pale skin and in this photo my hair is dark. Banner image is of a stack of old books with different colored covers, including red, ivory, and dark green.<\/span><\/p>"],"url":["https://firefish.lgbt/@nixkelley"],"avatar":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/avatars/110/744/751/894/024/014/original/26ba613258faf554.png"],"avatar_static":["https://files.mastodon.social/cache/accounts/avatars/110/744/751/894/024/014/original/26ba613258faf554.png"],"header":["https:/